1.11
log
@convert to new .Dd format;
@
text
@.\" $OpenBSD: pcdisplay.4,v 1.10 2004/09/30 19:59:25 mickey Exp $
.\" $NetBSD: pcdisplay.4,v 1.3 2000/05/13 15:22:17 mycroft Exp $
.\"
.\" Copyright (c) 1999
.\" 	Matthias Drochner.  All rights reserved.
